page.title: 08MY TYPICAL DAY
page.content: My typical day begins with me getting up at 8:00 am and having my breakfast which consits of weetabix and a cup of tea.At 8:30 am I leave for school. We have 8 lessons at school,4 in the morning and 4 in the afternoon.We start school at 8:50 and have registration where the teacher takes names of all the class.We have lunch at 12:00 for 60 minutes.We start school again at 1:00 then we have afternoon registration. We go home at 3:30.I get home about 3:45 i do my homework and then go out till 5:30 and then i have my dinner. I go out till 9:00 then come in.I goto bed about 10:00. BY SUSIE PRATLEY.
